textPage.text1: We aim to make renting with us as profitable and easy for you as possible.
textPage.text2: Certain rental terms have fixed rates.
textPage.text3: If the purpose of your rental does not fit any tariff.
textPage.text4: We offer a simple and flexible pricing system:
textPage.li1: Short-term (3-7 days): 30% discount off the base daily rate.
textPage.li2: More than a week (7-30 days): 50% discount off the base daily rate.
textPage.li3: Long-term (more than 30 days): 85% discount off the base daily rate.
